<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bali Island</title>

    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png">
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#da532c">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/css_home/libs.bundle.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/css_home/theme.bundle.css" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav.navbar {
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
            background-color: transparent !important;
            padding-top: 0 !important;
        }

        nav.navbar .nav-link,
        nav.navbar .navbar-brand,
        nav.navbar i,
        nav.navbar span {
            color: #ffffff !important;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav.navbar:hover {
            background-color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        nav.navbar:hover .nav-link,
        nav.navbar:hover .navbar-brand,
        nav.navbar:hover i,
        nav.navbar:hover span {
            color: #000000 !important;
        }

        .bali-content {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 150px auto 50px auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .bali-image {
            flex: 0 0 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .bali-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        .bali-text {
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .bali-video {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        .bali-video iframe {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .wanttogo-btn button {
            border: 2px solid #5d3eff;
            color: #5d3eff;
            background: transparent;
            border-radius: 0;
            padding: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .wanttogo-btn button:hover {
            background-color: #5d3eff;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg border-0 position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 z-index-30">
    <div class="w-100 pb-lg-0 pt-lg-0 pt-4 pb-3">
        <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap">

            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold fs-3 m-0 p-0 flex-shrink-0" href="/home">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <span class="fs-5">Bali</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <div class="ms-5 flex-shrink-0 collapse navbar-collapse navbar-collapse-light w-auto flex-grow-1" id="navbarNavDropdown">
                <ul class="navbar-nav py-lg-2 mx-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item me-lg-4"><a class="nav-link fw-bolder py-lg-4" href="/home">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item me-lg-4"><a class="nav-link fw-bolder py-lg-4" href="/wanttogo">Want To Go</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item dropdown me-lg-4">
                        <a class="nav-link fw-bolder dropdown-toggle py-lg-4" href="#" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">Categories</a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/hiking">Hiking</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/islands">Islands</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/cities">Cities</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="bali-content">
    <div class="bali-image">
        <img src="/images/bali.png" alt="Bali Island">

        <!-- ✅ FIXED FORM -->
        <form method="POST" action="/want-to-go" class="wanttogo-btn">
            <input type="hidden" name="slug" value="bali">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm w-100">
                Add to Want to Go
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="bali-text">
        <p>
            Also known as the Land of the Gods, Bali appeals through its sheer natural beauty of looming
            volcanoes and lush terraced rice fields that exude peace and serenity. It is also famous as a surfers' paradise.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bali-video">
        <iframe height="315"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BFS9n4B_2xA"
                title="YouTube video player"
                allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/javascript/js_home/vendor.bundle.js"></script>
<script src="/javascript/js_home/theme.bundle.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
